Iwe uchagamuchira ruoko apo munyengetero uchange uchienderera mberi.

0:00:24.920,0:00:30.380
Kwete vanhu vari pano chete asiwo vatariri mudzimba dzavo, pasi rose.

0:00:30.380,0:00:36.960
Iwe une huvepo hwe "kubatwa" pauri.

0:00:36.960,0:00:48.480
