0:03:01.940,0:03:18.780
Ndiri kureva, Mweya wa Baba, Mweya wa Mwari, Ishe wedu Jesu - Haagare pa Anoshungurudzika.

0:03:18.780,0:03:21.620
Achaburuka.

0:03:21.620,0:03:27.340
Regai simba ra She riburuke.

0:03:27.340,0:03:29.520
Izwi raenda.

0:03:29.520,0:03:31.760
Kupi? KuDenga.

0:03:31.760,0:03:37.140
Denga richange richiongorora kuti izwi raani.

0:03:37.140,0:03:40.320
Ehe hongu - uyu muranda wedu.

0:03:40.320,0:03:41.880
Zvakanaka, regai tiende.

0:03:41.880,0:03:45.240
Vanotevera izwi racho zvakare, pasi.

0:03:45.240,0:03:48.020
Mhepo inobva yashanduka.

0:03:48.020,0:03:54.740
Denga rinenge richitarisa vanhu vakagadzirira kumugamuchira Iye.

0:03:54.740,0:04:01.220
Haagare muvanhu kana Akashungurudzika.

0:04:01.220,0:04:03.280
Iwe unofanirwa kuisa izvozvo mupfungwa dzako.

0:04:03.280,0:04:07.080
Mufundisi wako paanenge achidana ungano kumunamato - iwe unofanira kugadzirira.

0:04:07.080,0:04:13.700
Kana akabudirira kudana Mweya Mutsvene, haagoni kumudzivirira.

0:04:13.700,0:04:20.280
Anogona kungodana chete uye Mweya Mutsvene achatsvaga avo vakanyatsomugadzirira.

0:04:20.280,0:04:23.980
Haagare apo Anoshungurudzika.

0:04:23.980,0:04:37.260
Tinoshungurudza Mweya Mutsvene kuburikidza nekuzvikudza kwedu uye tinoratidza kuzvikudza kwedu nenzira dzakasiyana siyana.

0:04:37.260,0:04:42.760
Munhu wose anoziva kuti kana murume achizvikudza anoita seizvi.

0:04:42.760,0:04:44.960
Unobva wati: - Murume uyu anozvikudza.

0:04:44.960,0:04:46.740
Upi? - Uyo ari kuuya.

0:04:46.740,0:04:52.060
Iwe uchaona murume akadai.

0:04:52.060,0:04:57.540
Murume iyeye anozvikudza zvikuru - acharatidzika seizvi.

0:04:57.540,0:04:58.460
Hazvisi zvechokwadi here?

0:04:58.460,0:05:06.920
Iwe unozviona sekuzvikudza asi iwe hauzivi kuti pane nzira dzakasiyana siyana dzatinogona kuratidza kudada kwedu.

0:05:06.920,0:05:08.260
Handiyo nzira chete.

0:05:08.260,0:05:10.940
Pane nzira dzakasiyana siyana dzatinokwanisa kuzviradza nadzo.

0:05:10.940,0:05:13.600
Chero nguva kubva ikozvino iwe uchaona zvichazoitika.

0:05:13.600,0:05:20.060
Unonzwa vamwe vanhu vachiseka vamwe, "O Mwari wangu, tarisai munhu uyu, adonhera pasi".

0:05:20.060,0:05:23.440
Asi iye pachake haana kudonha.

0:05:23.440,0:05:31.620
Kana iwe usingawi uye mumwe munhu achiwa, sei iwe uchitaura nezvemunhu uyu awa?

0:05:31.620,0:05:37.820
Haisi nyn'mbo.

0:05:37.820,0:05:40.060
Ino ichechi ya Mwari.

0:05:40.060,0:05:45.160
Gadzirira iwe pachako.

0:05:45.160,0:05:48.760
Rega Mweya wa Baba ugare mauri.

0:05:48.760,0:05:58.720
Anoda kuva Iye mbune mauri; Haadi kuti iwe umuraire Iye.

0:05:58.720,0:06:04.340
Anoda kuva Iye mbune mauri.

