Anoda kuva Iye mbune mauri.

0:06:21.060,0:06:33.440
Kunyangwe Ari kushandisa chimiro chako, nhengo dzako, muviri wako, zvakadaro, Anoda kuva Iye mbune.

0:06:33.440,0:06:35.260
Ndeapi matambudziko ako?

0:06:35.260,0:06:38.520
Ndezvipi zvinhu zvinoshungurudza?

0:06:38.520,0:06:46.280
Kana ini ndikachengeta chigumbu, ndatoshungurudza Mweya Mutsvene.

