0:06:51.740,0:06:52.980
Zvakare

0:06:52.980,0:06:56.340
Kana ini ndikachengeta chigumbu, ndatoshungurudza Mweya Mutsvene.

0:06:56.340,0:07:06.820
Hazvinei kuti watadza here kana kuti wagona, nokuda kwechikonzero chipi nechipi, semuKristu - pandinongo chengeta chigumbu pamusoro pako,

0:07:06.820,0:07:12.080
Ndatotambudza Mweya Mutsvene.

0:07:12.080,0:07:15.380
Wakachengeta chigumbu here?

0:07:15.380,0:07:16.940
Marwadzo akare?

0:07:16.940,0:07:24.100
Inzwa wakasununguka zvino; ingoti mumwoyo mako uchirevesa, "Ndinokanganwira murume uya, ndinokanganwira mukadzi uya."

0:07:24.100,0:07:25.800
Tanga kuropafadza vanhu vako.

0:07:25.800,0:07:28.400
Varopafadze.

0:07:28.400,0:07:33.180
Zvapfuura kwandiri - kwete, ndine urombo, Mwari.

0:07:33.180,0:07:39.220
Ishe, mundiregerere ini sezvandinoregerera avo vakanditadzira ini.

0:07:39.220,0:07:44.620
Saka, tanga ikozvino, tisati tadana Denga.

0:07:44.620,0:07:53.620
Apo Denga rinoburuka, Mweya wa Baba, Haagari mumunhu anochengeta chigumbu.

0:07:53.620,0:07:56.920
Ndicho chikonzero iwe uchifanira kuzvichenesa ikozvino.

0:07:56.920,0:08:03.120
Murume bofu uyo asingagoni kuona, achatanga kuti, "Ndave kuona!"

0:08:03.120,0:08:13.460
Iwe uchati, "Zvinhu zvose zviri kuitika panzvimbo yakandipoteredza, Asi zvakarongwa here? Uko, Kurutsa, ropa, makonye, zvipembenene.

0:08:13.460,0:08:19.460
Chii chanetsa? Izvi hazvishandi kwandiri. "

0:08:19.460,0:08:31.340
Apo Denga - kureva kuti, Mweya wa Baba - wauya, Haashandi mumunhu akachengeta chigumbu.

0:08:31.340,0:08:36.280
Haagare apo Anoshungurudzika.

0:08:36.280,0:08:41.020
Tinogona kumushungurudza chete apo tinochengeta chigumbu pamusoro pe hama yedu.

0:08:41.020,0:08:45.180
Munhu wose anochengeta zvigumbu.

0:08:45.180,0:08:51.800
Hapana munhu mumwe chete pano anogona kusimuka achiti, "Kwete, ndakasununguka kubva kune izvi".

0:08:51.800,0:08:57.080
Vanhu vachakuudza kuti vakanga vakarwadziswa, vasina kururamisirwa:

0:08:57.080,0:09:01.300
"Handina mhosva asi izvi ndizvo zvavakaita kwandiri. Ini handifari."

0:09:01.300,0:09:06.880
Iwe uri kuchengeta chigumbu; kwete kune mumwe munhu asi kwauri pachako.

0:09:06.880,0:09:12.520
Mweya wako haugone kusununguka kana iwe usingafari.

0:09:12.520,0:09:17.060
Waona Mwari se akavimbika.

0:09:17.060,0:09:21.400
Kana iwe uchiziva kuti Mwari akavimbika, chii chimwe zvakare?

0:09:21.400,0:09:26.100
Iwe unotanga kuvimba Naye!

0:09:26.100,0:09:28.620
Izvo ndizvo zvinoreva 'kuvimbika'.

0:09:28.620,0:09:39.400
Panguva iyo iwe unoziva kuti Iye akatendeka, unotanga kuvimba Maari ne kutemba naye.

0:09:39.400,0:09:45.020
Simuka tinyengetere.

0:09:45.020,0:09:55.680
Tiri pano kuti tirwise chinhu chipi zvacho chisiri cha Mwari.

0:09:55.680,0:10:05.100
Zvinhu izvozvo ndizvo zvinokonzera dambudziko ne njodzi dzauinadzo nhasi,

0:10:05.100,0:10:11.360
Nokudaro, rega Mwari pachake, Jesu, atipe Shoko rokuti titaure.

0:10:11.360,0:10:15.780
Kana ndikakubvumira kuti utange kunyengetera ...

0:10:15.780,0:10:18.200
Kune zvinhu zvakawanda zvaunoda kunyengeterera nezvazvo.

0:10:18.200,0:10:20.080
Zvakawanda kwazvo.

0:10:20.080,0:10:23.900
Iwe unoti, "Ndinotsiura uyu" ...

0:10:23.900,0:10:26.280
Kune zvinhu zvakawanda zvaunoda kutsiura.

0:10:26.280,0:10:29.560
Hatigoni kunamata; Mweya Mutsvene ndiye anotipa Shoko.

0:10:29.560,0:10:35.100
Paanotipa Shoko mumunamato, unobva wave mutauro wemunamato.

0:10:35.100,0:10:36.180
Chii chemunyengetero?

0:10:36.180,0:10:37.740
(Mutauro.)

0:10:37.740,0:10:41.920
Iwe hauzive kuti munyengetero une mutauro wawo.

0:10:41.920,0:10:45.800
Mweya Mutsvene, ndipei Shoko; Handizivi kunyengetera - Mweya Mutsvene anondipa.

0:10:45.800,0:10:49.400
Pane chipingamupinyi pakati pako na Mwari.

0:10:49.400,0:11:01.380
Pane rusvingo, rwusingakubvumire kuti uone Mwari,unzwe Mwari kana kunzwa zve nzvimbo ye huvepo hwa Mwari.

0:11:01.380,0:11:03.960
Chimwe chinhu chiri pakati pako na Mwari.

0:11:03.960,0:11:05.820
Uyu ndiwo mupingo.

0:11:05.820,0:11:17.180
Zvinogona kuve kuchengeta zvigumbu, miedzo, mweya usingaregereri kana marwadzo enguva yakapfuura.

0:11:17.180,0:11:20.240
Iwe unoramba kuzvirega zvichipfuura.

0:11:20.240,0:11:26.700
Kana iwe usingaregi zuro achipfuura, haugoni kufara nhasi.

0:11:26.700,0:11:29.740
Ndizvo zvaunazvo muchikoro - kudzokorora.

0:11:29.740,0:11:32.860
Mutauro iwoyo hauna kunaka - kudzokorodza.

0:11:32.860,0:11:40.200
Vazhinji vedu takazara nezva zuro asi tinoda kufara nhasi - hazvigoneki.

0:11:40.200,0:11:41.120
Udza waugere naye.

0:11:41.120,0:11:50.340
Iwe uzere nezva zuro asi unoda kufara nhasi - hazvibviri.

0:11:50.340,0:11:53.940
Kuzadzwa nezvazuro ndikokufunga nezvekare zvako.

0:11:53.940,0:11:59.620
Kana iwe uzere nezvinhu zvakanaka zvazuro, iwe unogona kufara nhasi.

0:11:59.620,0:12:04.080
Asi hazvisi zvinhu zvakanaka; zvakaipa zvazvo ndizvo zvauri kufunga nezvazvo.

0:12:04.080,0:12:07.460
